
* Changes from 0.1.0 to 0.9.0
  - openmpi support out of the box
  - MPI errors are reported via Common Lisp conditions
  - improved testsuite
  - MPI operations operate very efficiently on simple-arrays (including
    strings!)
  - added a benchmark suite

* Current TODO
** parallel IO

* Testing

  mpirun -np 2 sbcl --noinform --quit --eval "(asdf:test-system :cl-mpi)" --eval "(mpi:mpi-finalize)"

  mpirun -np 2 sbcl --noinform --quit --disable-debugger --eval "(asdf:test-system :cl-mpi-benchmarks)" --eval "(mpi:mpi-finalize)"

  mpirun -np 2 sbcl --noinform --quit --disable-debugger --load ~/userdata/proj/cl-mpi/mpi-benchmarks/run.lisp --eval "(mpi:mpi-finalize)"

